StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetMapsSectorsByZipCode]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@ZipCode varchar(5) AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT ms.SectorID AS SectorID, ms.Recrui.ngOrganiza.onId AS Recrui.ngOrganiza.onId, ms.SectorDesignator AS SectorDesignator, ms.LastUpdateDate AS LastUpdateDate, ms.LastUpdateUserId AS LastUpdateUserId, ms.SectorType FROM [usmc].[MapsSectorZip] msz INNER JOIN [usmc].[MapsSector] ms ON msz.SectorID = ms.SectorID
WHERE msz.Zip = @ZipCode
END
